Class: Bot

Bot

Class to ineract with Discord

new Bot(key)

Parameters:
Name Type Description
key string Discord Bot Key
Properties:
Name Type Description
key string The Bot's Discord Key
botInfo BotInfoObject Information about the bot
disnode Disnode Disnode Refrence
shardID string Bot's Shard ID
totalShards string Total number of shards
lastS string Last 's' sent in a WS Packet (internal use mostly)
guilds Object.<GuildObject> The Guilds the bot belonds to. Object so access via `this.disnode.bot.guilds[guildID]`
channels Object.<ChannelObject> All the channels. Object so access via `this.disnode.bot.channels[channelID]`
users Object.<UserObject> All the users. Object so access via `this.disnode.bot.users[userID]`
